OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776819790
OL,3,CCole-Hamilton having time of his life
OL,4,Cas Lib Dems seek best-ever Holyrood
OL,5,Cresult
OL,7,FScottish Liberal Democrat leader Alex
OL,8,FCole-Hamilton says he is having the
OL,9,Ftime of his life in the Holyrood
OL,10,Felection ` insisting that his party is
OL,11,F"in the mix" with voters "for the
OL,12,Ffirst time in a long time".
OL,14,FMr Cole-Hamilton says he has knocked
OL,15,Fon "more doors than any other party
OL,16,Fleader in Scotland" in the run-up to
OL,17,Fpolling day on May 7 ` but in a bid to
OL,18,Fget his message across further, he has
OL,19,Falso taken part in a mix of themed
OL,20,Fphotocalls.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@LO]sD@ZOUtD@ZO]wD@DOUxD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776819790
OL,3,CCole-Hamilton having time of his life
OL,4,Cas Lib Dems seek best-ever Holyrood
OL,5,Cresult
OL,7,FAs part of these, Mr Cole-Hamilton has
OL,8,Fsped down the River Clyde in a
OL,9,Fspeedboat, played tennis with UK
OL,10,FLiberal Democrat leader Sir Ed Davey,
OL,11,Fmade mocktails with peaches ` to
OL,12,Fhighlight the importance of the peach-
OL,13,Fcoloured regional list ballot paper `
OL,14,Fand joined in with a dance class.
OL,16,F"I have been having the time of my
OL,17,Flife," the Scottish Liberal Democrat
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,26,@xD@AOUyD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776819790
OL,3,CCole-Hamilton having time of his life
OL,4,Cas Lib Dems seek best-ever Holyrood
OL,5,Cresult
OL,7,FThese visits allow him to meet "people
OL,8,Fwho are passionate about what they do"
OL,9,Fwhile also learning about "what is not
OL,10,Fworking for them at the moment".
OL,12,FHe is fighting his first Holyrood
OL,13,Felection campaign as leader after
OL,14,Ftaking over at the helm of the party
OL,15,Fin the wake of the 2021 Scottish
OL,16,FParliament vote when the party won
OL,17,Ffour seats.
OL,19,FA defection from the Tories took his
OL,20,Fparty's numbers up to five by the time
OL,21,FHolyrood broke up for the election.
OL,26,@oD@`OUpD@fO]qD@[OUrD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776819790
OL,3,CCole-Hamilton having time of his life
OL,4,Cas Lib Dems seek best-ever Holyrood
OL,5,Cresult
OL,7,FMr Cole-Hamilton believes his party
OL,8,Fcan build on the 2024 UK election
OL,9,Fresults, when they won six
OL,10,Fconstituencies north of the border,
OL,11,Fbeating the Tories and coming within
OL,12,F"touching distance" of the SNP ` with
OL,13,FJohn Swinney's party seeing its number
OL,14,Fof MPs at Westminster fall from 48 to
OL,15,Fnine.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776819790
OL,3,CCole-Hamilton having time of his life
OL,4,Cas Lib Dems seek best-ever Holyrood
OL,5,Cresult
OL,7,FSpeaking to the Press Association, the
OL,8,FScottish Liberal Democrat said: "We're
OL,9,Fcoming into this election off the back
OL,10,Fof our best general election result in
OL,11,F100 years, we trebled our seats in
OL,12,FScotland, we overtook the Tories and
OL,13,Fwe came within touching distance of
OL,14,Fthe SNP."
OL,16,FLooking ahead to May 7, he adds he is
OL,17,F"really excited about how we are going
OL,18,Fto do".
OL,26,@pD@aOUvD@IO]yD@AOUzD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776819790
OL,3,CCole-Hamilton having time of his life
OL,4,Cas Lib Dems seek best-ever Holyrood
OL,5,Cresult
OL,7,FMr Cole-Hamilton believes his party
OL,8,Fcan win the 10 constituency seats they
OL,9,Fare targeting and can also return an
OL,10,FMSP in all eight of the areas on the
OL,11,Fregional list vote.
OL,13,FIf the Lib Dems could return 18 MSPs,
OL,14,Fthat would be the party's best-ever
OL,15,Fresult at Holyrood, topping the 17
OL,16,FMSPs elected in 1999 and 2003, when
OL,17,Fthey formed a coalition with Scottish
OL,18,FLabour.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776819790
OL,3,CCole-Hamilton having time of his life
OL,4,Cas Lib Dems seek best-ever Holyrood
OL,5,Cresult
OL,7,FPolls for the Holyrood election
OL,8,Fcontinue to point to the SNP being the
OL,9,Flargest party after next month's
OL,10,Fballot ` but the Liberal Democrat
OL,11,Fleader adds that it is "tight amongst
OL,12,Fthe other parties".
OL,14,FHowever, he insists the Lib Dems "are
OL,15,Fin the mix in that, for the first time
OL,16,Fin a long time", adding his party
OL,17,F"will be a much stronger voice in the
OL,18,Fnew parliament to come".
OL,26,@sD@XOUtD@RO]vD@bOUxD@OO]yD@AOUzD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776819790
OL,3,CCole-Hamilton having time of his life
OL,4,Cas Lib Dems seek best-ever Holyrood
OL,5,Cresult
OL,7,FIt comes as he accepts that "most
OL,8,Fpeople" in Scotland are "scunnered"
OL,9,Fwith politics.
OL,11,FWith the SNP having been in power for
OL,12,F19 years, he says that "wherever I go
OL,13,Fpeople I meet on the doorsteps who
OL,14,Fhave traditionally been SNP voters who
OL,15,Fare really struggling to find reasons
OL,16,Fto vote for them this time".
OL,26,@oD@]OUpD@GO]pD@YOUpD@cO]tD@XOUxD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776819790
OL,3,CCole-Hamilton having time of his life
OL,4,Cas Lib Dems seek best-ever Holyrood
OL,5,Cresult
OL,7,FMr Cole-Hamilton adds that people "are
OL,8,Fnot inspired by John Swinney, they
OL,9,Fdon't want to reward 19 years of
OL,10,Ffailure with a third decade ` a third
OL,11,Fdecade ` of SNP administration".
OL,13,FWhile support for Reform UK is on the
OL,14,Frise ` with some polls suggesting the
OL,15,Fparty could come in second ` the
OL,16,FLiberal Democrat says people "don't
OL,17,Fneed to settle for that mean-spirited
OL,18,Fworld view that Nigel Farage offers".
OL,20,FInstead, he argues his party offers "a
OL,21,Fbetter future, a brighter future".
OL,26,@oD@cOUsD@_O]xD@^OUzD@dO]|D@eOU}D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776819790
OL,3,CCole-Hamilton having time of his life
OL,4,Cas Lib Dems seek best-ever Holyrood
OL,5,Cresult
OL,7,FMr Cole-Hamilton says: "We have
OL,8,Fattacked this campaign with relentless
OL,9,Fpositivity, we have resisted the urge
OL,10,Fto get stuck into the pile-ons and
OL,11,Fscandal baiting that we have seen.
OL,13,F"We just want to present a positive
OL,14,Fvision for Scotland, which improves
OL,15,FScottish education by taking mobile
OL,16,Fphones out of classrooms and putting
OL,17,Fpupil support assistants in, which
OL,18,Fdrives down people's fuel bills with
OL,19,Fan emergency insulation programme or
OL,20,Fhelping them at the petrol pump."
OL,26,@oD@XOUuD@AOU|D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776819790
OL,3,CCole-Hamilton having time of his life
OL,4,Cas Lib Dems seek best-ever Holyrood
OL,5,Cresult
OL,7,FGoing into the election, he says the
OL,8,FLib Dems have "knocked more doors in
OL,9,Fthe last three months than we have
OL,10,Fever knocked as a party before",
OL,11,Fadding: "In Edinburgh last week, in
OL,12,Fjust one day we spoke to 800 people.
OL,14,F"That's the quantum of effort we're
OL,15,Fputting into it and we expect to be
OL,16,Frewarded at the ballot box."
OL,18,FSpeaking about himself, Mr Cole-
OL,19,FHamilton added: "I think it's fair to
OL,20,Fsay I do knock more doors than any
OL,21,Fother party leader in Scotland.
OL,26,@pD@OOUrD@_O]sD@IOUvD@AOUxD@\O]{D@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776819790
OL,3,CCole-Hamilton having time of his life
OL,4,Cas Lib Dems seek best-ever Holyrood
OL,5,Cresult
OL,7,F"It's almost an obsession, I get a
OL,8,Fchemical response from it now, it's
OL,9,Fsomething I am just not happy unless
OL,10,FI'm doing."
OL,12,FWhile he is happy to speak to voters
OL,13,Fon the doorsteps, he says he no longer
OL,14,Flooks at the comment sections on his
OL,15,Fsocial media.
OL,17,FIn 2024 he spoke out about seeking
OL,18,Fhelp in therapy for online abuse and
OL,19,Fhe still believes that politics can be
OL,20,F"brutal".
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@KO]|D@AOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776819790
OL,3,CCole-Hamilton having time of his life
OL,4,Cas Lib Dems seek best-ever Holyrood
OL,5,Cresult
OL,7,FHe states: "I just don't look at the
OL,8,Fcomment sections on my social media
OL,9,Fposts, but it is brutal, it is rough.
OL,11,F"Politics is a blood sport, but I
OL,12,Fchannel that now.
OL,14,F"There was a time when I was
OL,15,Fstruggling with it but now I'm like
OL,16,F'I'm not going to surrender the
OL,17,Fcountry I love to this kind of person'.
OL,19,F"I stand up to bullies, Lib Dems
OL,20,Falways stand up to bullies."
OL,26,@oD@LOUsD@AOUvD@AOU{D@AOU|D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/13
